window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She walks in on me banging another woman.</p> <p>One sniff in her direction, and I know she's mine.</p> <p>Scenting his fated mate, my wolf awakens and roars with lust.</p> <p>But Tessa Morrigan can't be my queen.</p> <p>She came too late.</p> <p>I've started the Underworld Bride Trials. All the women must fight to the death until the last one stands by my side.</p> <p><b>This spicy enemies-to-lovers paranormal romance boxed set includes all four books:</b></p> <p>Book 1: <i>Playboy King</i></p> <p>Book 2: <i>Rejected Queen</i></p> <p>Book 3: <i>Hidden Court</i></p> <p>Book 4: <i>Hellfire Crown</i></p>"; 
